Install Base Targeting: Prospecting From Your Competitors' Customers
One of the most underutilized prospecting strategies in B2B lead generation is install base targeting. The concept involves identifying companies that are currently using a competitor's technology or a complementary product and targeting them with messaging that speaks directly to why your solution offers a better fit.

This works because the prospect already understands the category. They are already paying for a solution that addresses the pain point yours solves. The conversation is not about convincing them they have a problem. It is about convincing them your solution solves that problem better.

Install base targeting data is available through specialized data providers that track technology usage across companies. Combined with intent signals and a compelling displacement message, it can be one of the highest-converting prospecting strategies available.

